---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="Steven Rawson — OT/ICS cybersecurity expert with CISSP, GICSP, GCWN certifications and a decade of critical infrastructure security experience.">

  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="mb-16">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-sky-800 bg-sky-950/50 text-sky-400 text-xs font-medium tracking-wider uppercase mb-6">
        About the Consultant
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Steven Rawson</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
        OT/ICS cybersecurity professional with over a decade of experience securing the systems that keep critical infrastructure running.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">

      <!-- Main bio -->
      <div class="md:col-span-2 space-y-6 text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          Steven Rawson has spent his career at the intersection of operational technology and cybersecurity — a niche that demands fluency in both the engineering systems that control physical processes and the security disciplines designed to protect them.
        </p>
        <p>
          His work at Idaho National Laboratory, the nation's premier nuclear and critical infrastructure security research institution, has provided rare insight into the vulnerabilities, attack patterns, and defensive architectures relevant to industrial control systems across every critical sector.
        </p>
        <p>
          Prior to INL, Steven served in the United States Navy, where he developed the operational discipline and mission-critical mindset that continues to shape his approach to security: understand the mission first, then protect it.
        </p>
        <p>
          An MBA alongside his technical credentials reflects a core belief — that security advice disconnected from business reality doesn't get implemented. Every recommendation Rawson Consulting delivers is scoped to operational constraints, risk tolerance, and organizational capacity.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Credentials sidebar -->
      <div class="space-y-8">

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest text-sky-400 uppercase mb-4">Certifications</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            {[
              { cert: 'CISSP', name: 'Certified Information Systems Security Professional' },
              { cert: 'GICSP', name: 'Global Industrial Cyber Security Professional' },
              { cert: 'GCWN', name: 'GIAC Certified Windows Security Administrator' },
            ].map(({ cert, name }) => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="mt-0.5 px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-xs font-bold bg-sky-900 text-sky-300 shrink-0">{cert}</span>
                <span class="text-slate-400 text-sm">{name}</span>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest text-sky-400 uppercase mb-4">Background</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-400">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-slate-600">▸</span> Idaho National Laboratory
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-slate-600">▸</span> United States Navy
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-slate-600">▸</span> MBA
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest text-sky-400 uppercase mb-4">Focus Areas</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-400">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-slate-600">▸</span> ICS / SCADA Security</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-slate-600">▸</span> OT Network Architecture</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-slate-600">▸</span> Critical Infrastructure Risk</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-slate-600">▸</span> Compliance Advisory</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="mt-20 pt-12 border-t border-slate-800 text-center">
      <p class="text-slate-400 mb-6">Interested in working together?</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block px-8 py-3 rounded-lg bg-sky-600 hover:bg-sky-500 text-white font-semibold transition-colors">
        Get in Touch
      </a>
    </div>

  </section>

</Layout>
